                "invention-title": [
                    "Green low-carbon salt chemical production method based on CO2 resource utilization",
                    "基于CO2资源化利用的绿色低碳盐化工生产方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a green low-carbon salt chemical production method based on CO2 resource utilization. The problems that in the prior art, CO2 emission reduction pressure is large, cross-industry multi-product technology and resource coupling development is difficult to conduct, cyclic comprehensive utilization of materials and energy is difficult to achieve, and a green low-carbon energy consumption system and a production system are difficult to construct are solved. The method comprises the following steps: capturing CO2, respectively electrolyzing water, water and salt water by green electricity to prepare H2, Cl2 and NaOH solutions, directly producing olefin by CO2 hydrogenation or producing methanol and then producing olefin, separating olefin to obtain ethylene and propylene, polymerizing propylene and ethylene to produce polypropylene, and producing polyvinyl chloride by chlorine and ethylene. Comprising a new energy power generation device, a salt water electrolysis device, a water electrolysis hydrogen production device, a carbon dioxide capture device, an olefin production device, a polypropylene production device, a polyvinyl chloride production device, a soda ash or baking soda production device and a coal-fired power plant. According to the invention, CO2 emission reduction and carbon neutralization can be realized, and chemical engineering and energy coupling development and industry fusion are realized."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了基于CO2资源化利用的绿色低碳盐化工生产方法，解决现有技术CO2减排压力大、难以跨行业多产品进行技术和资源耦合发展，难以实现物料和能源的循环综合利用，难以构建绿色低碳的能源消费系统和生产体系的问题。该方法为捕集CO2并以绿电分别电解水和水食盐水制H2、Cl2和NaOH溶液，CO2加氢直接生产烯烃或者生产甲醇再制烯烃，烯烃分离得乙烯和丙烯，丙烯和乙烯聚合生产聚丙烯，氯气和乙烯生产聚氯乙烯；包括新能源发电装置、食盐水电解装置、电解水制氢装置、二氧化碳捕集装置、制烯烃装置、制聚丙烯装置、制聚氯乙烯装置、生产纯碱或小苏打装置和燃煤电厂。本发明可实现CO2减排和碳中和，实现化工与能源耦合发展和行业融合。"
                }
            ]
